data.description: Amazing opportunity to own a 4 bedroom, 2.25 bath home in the much sought after College Estates area! Step through a gated courtyard to the faux double door entry. 3 bedrooms, full bath and en suite master with updated shower are to your left. To the right you will find the 2012 updated gourmet kitchen with 36' Wolf French Cooktop, 36' Miele double oven, Miele Futura Dimension dishwasher, and 36' Franke sink, open dining area, wine room (or walk-in pantry), laundry room, 1/4 bath and family room with fireplace and sliding glass doors to the rear yard with pond and 2 producing avocado trees.There is also an oversized converted garage off the courtyard with amazing stone fireplace that would make a perfect entertainment/game room!This 2028 square foot home has been updated over the years, so the big-ticket items are already done! Water heater installed 4/24/21, 3-ton furnace 12/8/17, roof replaced 10/14/11, dual pane windows & sliding glass doors installed 11/26/11, full copper plumbing, sewer line replaced to street in 2012, 220 electrical in garage, and fiberglass garage door allows light to the interior while keeping your belongings safe.Centrally located with something for everyone; Elmhurst elementary, Anacapa Middle School, Buena High. Ventura College and Camino Real Park with tennis courts, upcoming pickle ball courts, baseball and off leash dog area. Arroyo Verde Park is less than a mile away. Oh, and of course, the beach is only 3 miles away.Needs work but priced accordingly.Come make this your home sweet home.
